summary.span: 定義可由 .NET 指令碼引擎擲回的例外狀況集。

span.span: Defines the set of exceptions that can be thrown by a .NET script engine.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError AppDomainCannotBeSet = int32(-2146226176)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 無法設定應用程式定義域。Exception string: The application domain cannot be set. 擲回的方法或方法來設定受管理的引擎，例如 Visual Basic 或 JScript 指令碼引擎 AppDomain 選項的嘗試失敗時。Thrown by the method or the method when attempts fail to set the AppDomain option on a managed engine, such as the Visual Basic or JScript script engines. 受管理的指令碼引擎不支援使用自訂的應用程式定義域。Managed script engines do not support using custom application domains. 受管理的指令碼引擎一律會使用執行所在的應用程式定義域。Managed script engines will always use the application domain in which they are running.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError AppDomainInvalid = int32(-2146226175)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的應用程式網域無效。Exception string: The specified application domain is not valid. 擲回的方法或時嘗試設定不正確的 AppDomain 參考的方法。Thrown by the method or method when attempting to set an AppDomain reference that is not valid. 若要重設`AppDomain`選項為 null 參考，呼叫方法。To reset the `AppDomain` option to a null reference, call the method.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError ApplicationBaseCannotBeSet = int32(-2146226174)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 無法設定應用程式基底。Exception string: Application base cannot be set. 擲回的方法或時嘗試取得或設定 ApplicationBase 選項，在受管理的引擎，例如 Visual Basic.NET 或 JScript.NET 指令碼引擎的方法。Thrown by the method or method when attempts to get or set the ApplicationBase option on a managed engine, such as the Visual Basic .NET or JScript .NET script engines. 主機必須設定`ApplicationBase`它會建立其指令碼引擎的應用程式定義域中的選項。The host must set the `ApplicationBase` option in the application domain in which it creates its script engine.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError ApplicationBaseInvalid = int32(-2146226173)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的應用程式基底目錄無效。Exception string: The specified application base directory is not valid. 擲回的方法或方法時嘗試取得或設定 ApplicationBase 選項在引擎上，並由方法時指定為應用程式基底目錄的目錄不是有效的目錄。Thrown by the method or method when attempts to get or set the ApplicationBase option on an engine, and by the method when the directory specified as the Application Base directory is not a valid directory.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError AssemblyExpected = int32(-2146226172)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串：未參考有效的組件。Exception string: does not reference a valid assembly. 擲回的方法時的`IVsaReferenceItem`所包含的物件集合不是有效的組件。Thrown by the method when one of the `IVsaReferenceItem` objects contained in the collection does not represent a valid assembly.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError AssemblyNameInvalid = int32(-2146226171)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 組件名稱無效。Exception string: Assembly name is not valid. 擲回的屬性不是有效的組件名稱時指定物件。Thrown by the property when an assembly name that is not valid is specified for a object.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError BadAssembly = int32(-2146226170)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 組件的格式不正確。Exception string: Assembly format is not valid. 引擎提供的組件無效時擲回。Thrown when the assembly provided to the engine is not valid. 引擎會嘗試執行，或使用組件時，通常就會發生這個例外狀況。This exception typically occurs when an engine tries to run or use the assembly.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError BrowserNotExist = int32(-2146226115)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 找不到指定的瀏覽器。Exception string: The specified browser was not found. 已啟動遠端偵錯工作階段並嘗試啟動遠端瀏覽器，卻沒有瀏覽器 aDTEngine.AttachDebugger 方法所擲回。Thrown by the aDTEngine.AttachDebugger method when a remote debugging session has been initiated and an attempt made to launch the remote browser, but a browser is not available.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError CachedAssemblyInvalid = int32(-2146226169)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 無效的快取的組件。Exception string: The cached assembly is not valid. 擲回的方法時呼叫它和它嘗試使用先前的快取的組件，但組件無效，例如，它是 null 參考 (`Nothing`在 Visual Basic 中)。Thrown by the method when it is called and it tries to use a previously cached assembly, but the assembly is not valid, for example, it is a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError CallbackUnexpected = int32(-2146226168)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 無法在這個階段會進行回呼。Exception string: Callback cannot be made at this time. 多個方法時所擲回的或回呼方法在未預期的時間點呼叫。Thrown by multiple methods when one of the or callback methods is called at an unexpected time. 例如，方法只能呼叫引擎由於呼叫方法。For example, the method should only be called by an engine as a result of a call to the method. 如果呼叫任何其他時候，會擲回 CallbackUnexpected 例外狀況。If it is called at any other time, a CallbackUnexpected exception will be thrown.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError CannotAttachToWebServer = int32(-2146226100)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 無法將附加到指定的 Web 伺服器。Exception string: Cannot attach to the specified Web server. 啟動伺服器端偵錯工作階段和 VSA 無法偵錯工具附加至指定的 Web 伺服器時，aDTEngine.AttachDebugger 方法所擲回。Thrown by the aDTEngine.AttachDebugger method when launching a server-side debugging session and VSA cannot attach the debugger to the specified Web server.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError CodeDOMNotAvailable = int32(-2146226167)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 沒有有效的程式碼文件物件模型 (CodeDOM)。Exception string: A valid Code Document Object Model (CodeDOM) is not available. 擲回的屬性不是可讀取的屬性。Thrown by the property when the property is not available to be read. 引擎不支援屬性，或需要的明確呼叫方法，以產生文件物件模型 (DOM)。The engine either does not support the property or it requires an explicit call to the method in order to generate the Document Object Model (DOM).

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError CompiledStateNotFound = int32(-2146226166)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 無法載入指定的編譯的狀態。Exception string: The specified compiled state could not be loaded. 擲回的方法呼叫未不會編譯狀態引擎時。Thrown by the method when it is called for an engine that does not have compiled state.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError DebuggeeNotStarted = int32(-2146226114)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 偵錯目標應用程式未啟動。Exception string: Debug target application not started. Windows 用戶端偵錯工作階段開始時，aDTEngine.AttachDebugger 方法所擲回但`AttachDebugger`方法不能啟動使用 TargetEXE 選項指定的目標應用程式。Thrown by the aDTEngine.AttachDebugger method when a Windows client debugging session is initiated, but the `AttachDebugger` method is not able to launch the target application that is specified with the TargetEXE option.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError DebugInfoNotSupported = int32(-2146226165)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 不支援偵錯資訊的使用。Exception string: The use of debug information is not supported. 擲回的屬性設定為 true，但引擎時不支援產生偵錯資訊。Thrown by the property when it is set to true, but the engine does not support the generation of debugging information. 繼續編譯，但引擎會編譯程式碼沒有偵錯資訊。Compilation continues, but the engine compiles code without debug information.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError ElementNameInvalid = int32(-2146226164)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 項目名稱無效。Exception string: The element name is not valid. 擲回的方法和方法是呼叫與名稱參數不是有效的例如，一個包含無效的字元時。Thrown by the method and methods when either is called with a name parameter that is not valid, for example, one that contains characters that are not valid. 請注意，主機必須時擲回例外狀況 ElementNameInvalid 名稱參數為 null 指標，為 null 指標是用來要求引擎層級資料的有效引數。Note that the host must not throw an ElementNameInvalid Exception when the name parameter is a null pointer, as a null pointer is a valid argument used to request engine-level data.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError ElementNotFound = int32(-2146226163)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 找不到項目。Exception string: The element was not found. 擲回的方法呼叫時與名稱參數不是有效的也就是，沒有對應至先前儲存的項目。Thrown by method when it is called with a name parameter that is not valid, that is, one that does not correspond to a previously saved element.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineBusy = int32(-2146226162)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 引擎正忙於另一個執行緒。Exception string: Engine is busy servicing another thread. 當手寫筆引擎目前正在服務來自另一個執行緒的要求時，擲回的所有成員。Thrown by all members when an engine is currently servicing a request from another thread. 根據設計，.NET 指令碼引擎應該只從一個執行緒呼叫一次。By design, a .NET script engine should only be called from one thread at a time.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineCannotClose = int32(-2146226161)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 無法關閉指定的引擎。Exception string: The specified engine cannot be closed. 擲回的方法時嘗試呼叫這個方法，但。Thrown by method when an attempt is made to call this method, but the. NET 指令碼引擎無法正確關閉。NET script engine cannot be closed properly.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineCannotReset = int32(-2146226160)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 無法重設指定的引擎。Exception string: The specified engine cannot be reset. 擲回的方法時呼叫，但.NET 指令碼引擎無法重設或無法取消連結它的事件。Thrown by the method when it is called, but the .NET script engine could not be reset or its events could not be unhooked.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineClosed = int32(-2146226159)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 引擎已經關閉。Exception string: Engine has been closed. 已關閉.NET 指令碼引擎使用的呼叫之後，在大部分情況下擲回方法。Thrown in most cases after the .NET script engine has been closed using a call to the method. 一旦已呼叫關閉方法，無法再用引擎，和必須建立新的指令碼引擎，才能執行任何工作。Once the Close method has been called, the engine can no longer be used, and a new script engine must be created to perform any tasks.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineEmpty = int32(-2146226159)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的引擎具有可編譯的來源項目。Exception string: The specified engine has no source items to compile. 擲回的方法時呼叫，但沒有任何項目中的進行編譯時，也就是集合屬性 = 0。Thrown by the method when it is called, but there are no items in the collection to compile, that is, the property = 0.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineInitialized = int32(-2146226157)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 引擎已經初始化。Exception string: Engine has already been initialized. 擲回的方法和方法會呼叫這些方法，但尚未初始化.NET 指令碼引擎。Thrown by the method and methods when these methods are called but the .NET script engine has already been initialized. 如果主應用程式想要載入來源狀態或初始化新的指令碼引擎，相關的方法必須是在設定後呼叫的第一個項目 < xref:Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.IJSVsaEngine.RootMoniker\*If the host wants to load source state or initialize a new script engine, the respective methods must be the first ones called after setting the > 和屬性。and properties.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineNameInUse = int32(-2146226156)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的引擎名稱已在另一個引擎所使用。Exception string: The specified engine name is already in use by another engine. 擲回的屬性嘗試將它設定為相同的名稱時，現有的.NET 指令碼中主應用程式的引擎。Thrown by property when an attempt is made to set it to the same name as that of an existing .NET script engine inside the host. 而不需要是全域唯一的名稱屬性，它不能做為目前裝載的指令碼引擎的名稱相同。While the Name property does not need to be globally unique, it cannot be the same as the name of a script engine that is currently being hosted.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineNameInvalid = int32(-2146226113)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 引擎名稱無效。Exception string: Engine name not valid. 擲回的屬性，如果指定的名稱已在使用其他的引擎。Thrown by the property if the specified name is already in use by another engine. VSA 需要設計階段引擎名稱是唯一的。VSA requires that design-time engine names be unique.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineNameNotSet = int32(-2146226099)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 引擎名稱無效。Exception string: Engine name not valid. 擲回的屬性，如果指定的名稱已在使用其他的引擎。Thrown by the property if the specified name is already in use by another engine. VSA 需要設計階段引擎名稱是唯一的。VSA requires that design-time engine names be unique.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineNotCompiled = int32(-2146226155)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的引擎不會編譯。Exception string: The specified engine is not compiled. 擲回的方法和時沒有執行或儲存編譯的狀態的方法。Thrown by the method and methods when there is no compiled state to run or save. .NET 指令碼引擎必須編譯程式碼呼叫方法，或必須呼叫方法，然後才可以執行或儲存指令碼引擎。Either the .NET script engine must compile the code with a call to the method, or the method must be called before the script engine can be run or saved.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineNotExist = int32(-2146226112)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 引擎不存在。Exception string: Engine does not exist. 擲回的情況下 aIDE.ExtensibilityObject 屬性有任何有效的引擎從要擷取的擴充性物件。Thrown by the aIDE.ExtensibilityObject property in cases where there are no valid engines from which to retrieve the extensibility object.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineNotInitialized = int32(-2146226154)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的引擎未初始化。Exception string: The specified engine has not been initialized. 當.NET 指令碼引擎未正確初始化，且主應用程式嘗試存取的屬性或方法，會要求初始化指令碼引擎擲回多個成員。Thrown by multiple members when the .NET script engine has not been properly initialized, and the host tries to access a property or method that requires the script engine to be initialized.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineNotRunning = int32(-2146226153)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 必須執行指定的引擎。Exception string: The specified engine must be running. 擲回的方法和是稱為和指定的.NET 指令碼引擎不在執行時的屬性。Thrown by the method and property when either is called and the specified .NET script engine is not running.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EngineRunning = int32(-2146226152)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 引擎在執行中。Exception string: Engine is running. 當.NET 指令碼引擎正在執行，而且主應用程式嘗試執行指令碼引擎正在執行時，不允許的作業時擲回多個成員。Thrown by multiple members when the .NET script engine is running, and the host attempts to perform an operation that is not allowed while the script engine is running. 例如，嘗試建立新的程式碼項目使用引擎在執行中狀態時，方法會產生這個例外狀況。For example, attempting to create a new code item using the method will produce this exception if the engine is in the running state.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EventSourceInvalid = int32(-2146226151)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的事件來源不存在。Exception string: The specified event source does not exist. 擲回的不是有效的方法時呼叫的參數或參數的配對。Thrown by the method when it is called with a parameter or pairing of parameters that is not valid. 任一`itemName`參數是指主機沒有新增到引擎中的項目或`eventSourceName`參數指的是，事件來源已不會加入至指定的項目。Either the `itemName` parameter refers to an item that the host did not add to the engine, or the `eventSourceName` parameter refers to an event source that was not added to the specified item.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EventSourceNameInUse = int32(-2146226150)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的事件來源名稱已在使用。Exception string: The specified event source name is already in use. 擲回的方法的呼叫時`eventSourceName`先前已使用事件來源名稱為的參數。Thrown by the method when it is called with an `eventSourceName` parameter that has previously been used as an event source name.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EventSourceNameInvalid = int32(-2146226149)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的事件來源名稱無效。Exception string: The specified event source name is not valid. 擲回的方法和方法是呼叫時`eventSourceName`參數不是有效的識別項。Thrown by the method and methods when either is called with an `eventSourceName` parameter that is not a valid identifier. 主機可以判斷識別項是否為有效的第一個呼叫方法。Hosts can determine whether an identifier is valid by first calling the method.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EventSourceNotFound = int32(-2146226148)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 找不到指定的事件來源。Exception string: The specified event source not found. 擲回的方法的呼叫時`eventNameType`參數不是已做為事件來源中的程式碼項目。Thrown by the method when it is called with an `eventNameType` parameter that is not already in use as an event source in the code item.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError EventSourceTypeInvalid = int32(-2146226147)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 指定的事件來源類型不正確。Exception string: The specified event source type is not valid. 擲回的方法的呼叫時`eventSourceType`參數不是有效的型別。Thrown by the method when it is called with an `eventSourceType` parameter that is not a valid type. 請注意，這並非針對 Visual Basic 指令碼引擎，而是會報告在此情況下編譯例外狀況，則為 true。Note that this is not true for the Visual Basic script engine, which instead reports a compile exception in this situation.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 檔案是未知的類型。Exception string: File is of unknown type. 保留供未來使用。Reserved for future use.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError GetCompiledStateFailed = int32(-2146226146)

remarks.format: ## Remarks 例外狀況字串： 無法載入指定的編譯的狀態。Exception string: The specified compiled state could not be loaded. 擲回的方法和方法時`GetCompiledState`方法失敗。Thrown by the method and methods when the `GetCompiledState` method fails. Run 方法傳回給呼叫者`GetCompiledStateFailed`所傳回的例外狀況`GetCompiledState`方法。The Run method returns to the caller the `GetCompiledStateFailed` exception returned by the `GetCompiledState` method. `Run`如果組件快取會擲回的例外狀況，方法也可能產生 GetCompiledStateFailed 例外狀況。The `Run` method may also generate the GetCompiledStateFailed exception if the assembly cache throws an exception.

MemberSignature.Value: .field public static literal valuetype Microsoft.JScript.Vsa.JSVsaError GlobalInstanceInvalid = int32(-2146226145)
